<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The programmes of checks shall be organised and carried out in collaboration with the Member State concerned which shall appoint one or several experts for that purpose. </inglise>
