<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> A Member State in whose territory checks are carried out in accordance with this Decision shall provide the experts of the Commission and the experts appointed by the Commission with the assistance they require in order to perform their tasks. </inglise>
