<inglise> The Member State shall also give its comments as quickly as possible and in any case within ten working days of the receipt of the written report from the Commission. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriik esitab oma m&auml;rkused samuti v&otilde;imalikult kiiresti ja igal juhul k&uuml;mne t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast komisjoni kirjaliku aruande saamist. </eesti>
<inglise> In providing information on the findings of missions, the Commission shall in particular comply with the requirements laid down in Article 214 of the Treaty. </inglise>
